<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Automated Multi-Tier Web Application</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b,#334155);
color:white;
overflow:hidden;
}

.container{
width:900px;
padding:45px;
border-radius:20px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
text-align:center;
}

h1{
font-size:42px;
color:#38bdf8;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.subtitle{
font-size:18px;
color:#cbd5e1;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
gap:20px;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.card{
background:#111827;
padding:25px;
border-radius:15px;
}

.card h3{
color:#38bdf8;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.card p{
font-size:16px;
line-height:1.8;
color:#e2e8f0;
}

.tech{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:12px;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.tech span{
background:#2563eb;
padding:10px 18px;
border-radius:30px;
font-size:15px;
}

.footer{
border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
padding-top:20px;
font-size:18px;
}

.footer b{
color:#22c55e;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>🚀 Automated Multi-Tier Web Application</h1>

<div class="subtitle">
Fully Automated Infrastructure Deployment using Ansible on AWS
</div>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>Automation</h3>
<p>
Provisioned using<br>
Ansible Roles & Playbooks
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Infrastructure</h3>
<p>
AWS EC2<br>
Nginx • MariaDB • Docker
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Deployment</h3>
<p>
GitHub Version Control<br>
Automated Configuration
</p>
</div>

</div>

<div class="tech">

<span>Ansible</span>
<span>AWS EC2</span>
<span>Nginx</span>
<span>MariaDB</span>
<span>Docker</span>
<span>Git</span>
<span>GitHub</span>
<span>Linux</span>

</div>

<div class="footer">

<b>Created by Arun P S</b><br><br>

Cloud & DevOps Portfolio Project

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
